title: Mac DeMarco Discography
description:
Macbriare Samuel Lanyon "Mac" DeMarco (born Vernor Winfield Macbriare Smith IV, April 30, 1990) is a Canadian singer-songwriter, multi-instrumentalist and producer. He is best known for his solo career, during which he has released three full-length studio albums, Rock and Roll Night Club (2012), 2 (2012), and Salad Days (2014).
